#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:2
msgid "在线系统功能（Online System）"
msgstr "Online System"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:6
msgid "在线系统（多传送带 / 联机产线）相比离线系统提供额外的产线协同功能。本节内容仅在在线版本中显示。"
msgstr ""
"An online system (multi-conveyor / inline production) provides extra line-"
"coordination features beyond an offline system. This section is shown only "
"in the online edition."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:8
msgid "**包含的功能**"
msgstr "**What's included**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:10
msgid "多传送带并行检测与切换。"
msgstr "Parallel inspection across multiple conveyors, with switching."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:11
msgid "复检设备（review device）与主控设备分工。"
msgstr "Division of work between review devices and the main device."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:12
msgid "在线复检模式（检测到 NG 时暂停巡检、非阻塞模式）。"
msgstr "Online review modes (pause-on-NG patrol, non-blocking mode)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:13
msgid "工位间信号（上游 / 下游工位）。"
msgstr "Inter-station signaling (upstream / downstream stations)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/online/index.rst:17
msgid "本节仅适用于在线版本。离线版本不包含上述功能。"
msgstr ""
"This section applies only to the online edition. The offline edition does "
"not include these features."
